com.google.appinventor.client

Class OdeAsyncCallback<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appinventor.client.OdeAsyncCallback<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object returned by successful RPC call
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsyncCallback<T>

    public abstract class OdeAsyncCallback<T>
extends Object
implements AsyncCallback<T>
    Provides common functionality for asynchronous callbacks from the ODE client. Specifically, on failure, this does one of two things:
    1. If a failure message was provided during construction, it is displayed using ErrorReporter.reportError(String).
    2. Otherwise, if the no-args constructor was used, the message in the exception passed to onFailure(Throwable) is displayed using ErrorReporter.reportError(String).
